name: Pumpkin
description: Pumpkin is a meme coin deployed on Ethereum Mainnet. The total supply is 100,000,000,000 $PUMP and contract ownership is renounced. The tax for buys and sells is zero percent (0%). The project is community based and $PUMP tokens do not offer any intrinsic value. The initial funding happened through PinkSale and closed in $66,000 USD. $PUMP launched with an initial marketcap of $107,000 and the initial liquidity was $39,000 USD. The liquidity is locked on PinkLock for 180 days.
